# 🏢 Company OS
It is a scalable full-stack operating system developed for company management and communication. It combines task management, communication, meetings, leave processes, and organization management into a single platform.

---

# 🚀 Project Objectives
- Digitalize internal company processes
- Facilitate team communication
- Organize task and project tracking
- Centralize workflows

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

### Backend
- Go (Golang)
- REST + WebSocket architecture
- PostgreSQL
- RabbitMQ (event-driven structure)
- Elasticsearch
- Clean Architecture approach

### Frontend
- Next.js (React)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- App Router

### DevOps
- Docker
- Docker Compose

---

## 📦 Features

### 👥 Organization Management
- Company creation and management
- Department and role system
- Member invitation system

### 📋 Task System
- Project and task management
- Drag-and-drop board system
- Priority and status tracking

### 💬 Real-time Communication
- Chat system
- Notification system
- WebSocket-based structure

### 📅 Calendar & Meetings
- Meeting scheduling
- Calendar integration
- Reminder system

### 📝 Leave & Approval Processes
- Leave requests
- Multi-stage approval system
- Admin panel

### 📊 Activity Tracking
- User logs
- System event logs

---

## 🏗️ Architecture
The project is structured according to Clean Architecture principles:

- backend/
- ├── internal/
- │   ├── domain/
- │   ├── service/
- │   ├── adapter/
- │   └── config/
- ├── cmd/
- └── migrations/

---

⚙️ Setup

### 1. Cloning the repository
git clone https://github.com/hasretislerr/company-os.git
cd company-os

---

### 2. Running with Docker
docker-compose up --build

---

### 3. Running the Backend
cd backend
go mod tidy
go run main.go

---

### 4. Running the Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev

---

## 🌍 Environment Variables

- DB_HOST=localhost
- DB_PORT=5432
- DB_USER=postgres
- DB_PASSWORD=postgres
- DB_NAME=company_os
- JWT_SECRET=secret

